plot: The group worries about the hybrid baby's true nature, prompting Murphy to escape with his daughter.

Warren, Addy, 10k and Doc discuss about the true nature of Lucy: will she be the salvation of mankind or will she contribute to destroy mankind? Murphy feels that they are talking about Lucy and he flees with her. But before he asks Cassandra to keep them in the spot. Meanwhile Warren sees Vasquez sneaking around and she follows him. He goes to the direction of a group of Zero that subdues him. Warren decides to help him but they are wounded by bullets and run to a derelict hospital. Meanwhile Addy, 10k and Doc plot to escape from Cassandra running to different directions. Will they succeed? What is the secret of Vasquez?—Claudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
